{"tid":1596156,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家都是12歲 - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-09-26T11:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T14:53:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cda3ce11b260b9aa65c0a1132662bc092240a6d8","tid":1596156,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T11:48:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190926/20775025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190926%2F20775025&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAwzeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=cc503f33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190926%2F20775025&h=0154aa79\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190926/20775025</a><br />\n<br />\n大家都是12歲 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190926/large/1569423453_ebed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190926%2Flarge%2F1569423453_ebed.jpg&h=0dc60eee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n親戚的女兒12歲，手臂意外受傷，縫了8針。帶傷返學，在學校小休時被冒失的同學撞到傷臂，傷口的針線爆開，流了一地血。結果，有目擊的同學即場嘔吐、抽筋。學校要開動緊急機制，讓全班同學接受心理輔導。<br />\n<br />\n以上故事發生在加拿大，生活在文明法治國家的兒童，受高度保護，確保他們身心健康地成長，是政府責任，因為孩子，正是一個國家的未來。<br />\n<br />\n聽親戚講着這樣的故事，我的視線模糊起來，想起香港的孩子，過去100多天戰場歷練，已讓他們成為拆彈專家，習慣吸食過期催淚煙，習慣了肉體和精神的傷痛，見慣了鮮血和眼淚，習慣了被成年人以暴力對待。香港最小的「政治犯」，才13歲，因為攜帶觀星筆被濫捕。他們是香港的下一代，殘酷向他們施暴的，是香港政府、香港警隊。<br />\n<br />\n幾個月前，如果我在加拿大聽到同樣的故事，我不會有任何感覺，我知道文明社會是這樣運作的，每個孩子都該受到制度的保護。可是這一刻聽到，我有恍如隔世的感覺。香港，不知道受了甚麼詛咒，竟時空錯亂，去了錯誤的時間和空間。<br />\n<br />\n同一日，柒婆公開宣稱，被捕的1500人中，大部份是18歲以下的孩子，「我個人感覺心痛，因為他們都是孩子。」世上竟有如此歹毒的心腸，始作俑者說出這句話，比粗口更難聽。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n雙重依靠 (尊子)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n模範警嫂及其他 (邁克)"},{"pid":"8d3d4d2421e11da6954459b5daded6da8678f16f","tid":1596156,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T11:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c699d31f9cba007520480d7cceb7fbdac87461","tid":1596156,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T11:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69a0322e78ad80f89cef9ae0cc99c6033e1b98a","tid":1596156,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}